content.detailedDescription: My husband and i stepped outside to have a cigarette shortly before 2100 cdt on may 23 2017. there were dark rain clouds that looked like they would be coming towards from the south west. i pulled up a weather map on my phone which actually showed the weather moving away from us in the direction of the southwest. we both commented that it was strange weather to moving in that direction. i started staring into the clouds to see if i could visually tell that they were moving away in a southwest direction. all of the sudden a dimly glowing orange object entered my field of vision, from the east headed west, as i stared at the clouds. i asked my husband "what is that?" as i pointed at the object. he did not have a guess as to what it was. as we watched it fly through the lower thinner clouds it became very bright before disappearing into much thicker clouds. we could hear the sound of a plane/jet during the approximate 30 second siting but saw no aircraft through the clouds or below the clouds. a couple of minutes after we heard the sound of a second jet/plane possible headed west from the east but did not see the air craft though or below the clouds. given the sound of an aircraft and the sun setting in the west i wanted to write it off as a jet or plane but i am unaware of any aircraft that would reflect the sun so brightly and vibrantly across it's entire body.
content.summary: Bright orange object flying through clouds

content.detailedDescription:
This report is being submitted by michigan field investigator judith kulka, having received an email notice from the mimufon director and chief investigator the afternoon of 5/22/17 requesting that i follow up on a phoned report from witness glen bishop.  i reached glen this morning,5/23/17, and we spoke for about a half hour. [the only information i was originally given was that glen had pictures he'd taken of different unidentified objects in the air.]
this witness does not have internet access at this time, [thus the reason for fi submission of this report] but has a smart phone on which he can submit pictures to chief investigator
i'm focusing this report on the witness sighting of 5/14/17 that he photographed, and directed him to send the pictures to daniel snow, michigan chief investigator.
this witness reportedly has had many sightings since his first up close event in 1974 or 75.
[he at that time had possible missing time and unexplained marks on his arm.  there also was another witness of that event; it happened at a nursery in florida where they were both employed.]
the 5/14/17 event [the subject of this report] happened on a clear "blue" day in mid-afternoon in glen's north-facing back yard; it appeared as a very bright, stationary light.  he first looked at it through his binoculars, but it was too bright to look at, so he photographed it.
my second phone contact with the witness was this evening between 9-10:15 when i finished filling out the cms report and took more information about the witness and his sightings.
content.summary: Have had many sightings since 1974 or 75; this report is of a 5/14/17 sighting i shot photos of and am submitting to michigan chief investigator daniel snow.  it appeared as a very bright light in a cloudless sky in mid-afternoon; i could see figures.....

content.detailedDescription: While at the drive through at kfc. this homeless man pointed up towards this black triangle. so i had my cell phone in my hand and just as i started to record it spun in a circle. scared the heck out of me and the homeless man. i pulled out of the drive through and tried to catch more but it had vanished.
content.summary: I seen this while i was at the drive through of kfc on main st. winnipeg.

content.detailedDescription: Formation of golden lights observed over lake ontario.   lights where in 'v' shape pattern according to witnesses.   when i observed them,  the pattern seemed more random.  the oddest part is that they all disappeared 'instantly'.   i am familiar with 'flares' used by both us and canadian coast guards but never seen then in a tight formation or all 'burn out' at the exact same moment.   at first glance,  they appeared to be fireworks but they did not fade,   flutter,   descend...   i am started mostly by the fact that they all went away 'instantly'.
content.summary: Golden light emitting formation that changed and then instantly disappeared.  i spoke with viewers who took photo's which i would expect to be posted to internet.   plz have jan h call me as he knows me.

content.detailedDescription: I have yet again spotted and photographed an alien craft near a passenger plane over newton abbot. it was a beautiful hot day so i decided to go out in the hot sun and sky watch. i watched as many passenger planes passed over head i didn't see anything strange so then decided to focus my attention on planes in the distance. i spotted a passenger plane and began to watch and hoped to see something out of the ordinary, with that i spotted an alien craft that was moving up along the planes contrail towards the plane. once the alien craft was near to the passenger plane it matched the planes air speed and began to follow the plane. these alien crafts are checking out more and more passing aircraft's over this airspace. it is as if they are looking for someone or something. the mind really boggles to why they are so interested with our planes could some of these planes be carrying something else beside passengers? i continued to watch the plane and the alien craft as they flew across the sky. then after a while the alien craft seemed to lose interest with the plane and broke off it's pursuit and then flew off into nearby clouds away from prying eyes. the alien craft was oval shaped and was near enough the size of the passenger plane. another interesting thing to note is that there were also other smaller objects flying around in the sky. these objects were black and appeared to be spheres and were ejected by to the larger alien craft. it's truly bizarre. the photographs were taken on the 22 of ‎may ‎2017, ‏‎11:55 am at newton abbot devon england.
content.summary: Alien craft near passenger plane

content.detailedDescription: I was sky watching looking for anything out of the ordinary when my attention was drawn to a cloud that was shaped like a dragon. i was taking photographs when i notest a glint of light to the left of the dragon shaped cloud. i focused my attention to the area from where the glint had come from and to my surprise there was a craft of some type hovering there. the craft hovered there for a moment before it began to move. i watched as the strange craft started to ascend up into the sky and disappeared from sight. luckily i had been taking photographs of the dragon shaped cloud and i had managed to capture this alien craft. i took seven photographs that clearly show the movement of the craft as it ascended. on enlargement of the photographs i could see that the craft was oblong shaped and had a center light. there also appeared to be two black holes below the center light of the craft. what could they be? windows or vents?  i had previously photographed an identical looking object at the teign estuary could it of been the same craft. ‎it's very strange. the photographs were taken on the 10th of ‎april ‎2017 at newton abbot devon england.
content.summary: Alien craft with center light captured again

content.detailedDescription: I was at teignmouth taking random photographs and just happened to take a photograph of the railway line and cliff. to my surprise i appeared to have captured a ufo in the process. in the photograph the long ufo can clearly be seen in the distance above a field. when i took the photograph there was no aircraft's in the area so what could this long object be. the photograph was taken on the 16th of april 2017 2:48 pm at teignmouth devon england.
content.summary: Long ufo in the distance

content.detailedDescription: I was watching a propeller plane fly above the clouds when i spotted a black object that was emerging from the clouds. i quickly took a photograph and watched as the object went back into the clouds from where has emerged. ‎the photograph was taken on the 14th of ‎may ‎2017, ‏‎12:02 pm at newton abbot devon england.
content.summary: Black object emerging from the clouds

content.detailedDescription: On the 8th of ‎may ‎2017 at 1:31 pm i spotted a ufo that was going vertically up into the sky at great speed. i quickly took two photographs of the object. then at 1:44 pm i witnessed the same object coming back down vertically heading in the direction from where it had originally come from. i managed to take another two photographs that once again show the object in flight. the photographs were taken on the 8th of ‎may ‎2017 at newton abbot devon england. photograph one and two were taken at 1:31 pm while photograph three and four were taken at 1:44 pm. having witnessed many ufo on the same flight path going back and forth it leads me to believe that there must be an alien base somewhere in the vicinity. the area from where this ufo are emerging seems to be decoy country park. decoy country park has a very deep lake that was once a clay quarry. ball clay was found at decoy in the late 19th century and the clay was both mined and quarried at the site from 1850 until 1965. when the quarrying ceased the pit quickly filled with water and became the deep lake that we see today. i believe that these objects are going in and out of this lake undetected. i know for a fact that these alien craft have the ability to cloak and become completely invisible to the naked eye, furthermore they have the ability to enter the water without making a splash or any sound. i believe that there could be an alien base or a portal at the bottom of decoy lake and i also believe this is were the alien crafts are emerging from. decoy lake would be a great place to hide and be undetected. two years ago while investigating this area for any evidence of this i had an encounter with a pleiadian being. for me this is proof that aliens are in this area and that there is a base in the vicinity.
content.summary: Ufo going vertically up then vertically down

content.detailedDescription:
Filled out at mufon headquarters with witness on the phone, by field investigator l. flechtner 18809 on 5/23/2017. 
i realize this is very old sighting but we can look and see if any other sightings were reported in the surrounding area.
---------------------------------------------------------------
my two brothers and i were walking home in the woods at about dusk, on a path, single file. we looked up and saw the most beautiful green orb flying very slowly over us towards the west. it made a crackling sound like electricity and the green was colored like the inside of a kiwi fruit. it was almost dusk, so we could still see light and there was no moon. we panicked and ran for home. i don't remember how i got home, but i beat my brothers home, and mom was mad. it was fully dark. my two brothers came running out of the forest a second or two later. it seems we lost time since the moment we saw the green orb and started running. 
the trees we ran through were at least 30' high, and i don't remember seeing the orb disappear. 

my family was working the bean fields outside stayton, and we worked for a family named red and anna stanley. 

my brothers and i never talked about it until recently and i asked them what they remember. one brother said i wasn't with them and the other brother said i was with them, but they remember the green orb.

i heard a man on coast to coast talk about being abducted and how he thought he had an implant in his hand. a three dot mark on his right wrist between the thumb and wrist. 
that sounded familiar, i have had the same mark since i was six years old when i saw the green orb.
content.summary: My three brothers and i were walking on a path in the forest and we saw a beautiful green orb fly over us

content.detailedDescription: I was sky watching looking through my cameras viewfinder when i spotted a passenger plane that was flying in a northerly direction. i then spotted a large object that was behind the plane. the object appeared to be round shaped and was following the plane as it flew across the sky matching the plane airspeed. i started taking photographs and watched as the plane and the object flew off in to the distance and out of sight. the object was only visible through the camera viewfinder which was very perplexing. i find it very strange that some of these objects are using stealth technology to blend in to the sky and hide away from prying eyes while other objects are lit up like christmas trees and clearly want to be seen and make there present know. it's very odd. could this be two opposing alien forces, with one try to disclose to the people while the other wants to stay hidden for nefarious purpose. whatever these objects are i know that the government is well aware of their presents in the skies above us. the photograph was taken on the 8th of may 2017 at 11:25 am at newton abbot devon england.
content.summary: Large round object near passenger plane

content.detailedDescription: During the morning of may 5, 2017 i was taking pictures from the base of and across the street from the 360' free-standing microwave tower at the intersection of hanley and manchester roads. i wanted a good picture for a power point presentation. the next day i was editing the pics for clarity by zooming in. although my eyes had seen nothing but clear sky the previous morning, in two of the three pics there was a star-like image above and just right of the tower top. the three pics were taken 2 seconds apart; the image was not in the first pic but in the next two (see file 1). so within a 2 second time frame something wasn't there and then it was there for 2 seconds. seemed strange. noting that the second two pics were taken at 10:20am, i returned to the exact photo spot in the industrial park south of manchester rd. on may 7 at 10:30am and took a series of 12 tower photos spaced 2 seconds apart: the first pic had nothing but tower in it, however in the next 11 frames there were a total of 22 points of light. i have included frames 5 and 6 (files 2 & 3) where you can zoom into two lights directly over the tower in #5 and two seconds later in #6 they are gone but now there are two lights considerably right of the tower. i returned on may 9 at 10:20am and took a series of 10 pics, 2 seconds apart. seven of the frames had 9 lights.  i have included frames 1 and 2 where the light(s)  has a fuzzy quality (files 4 & 5). i returned at 10:20 on may 21, took 10 more pics and caught 4 more lights.  in summary, on 4 occasions i took a total of 35 pics and zoomed into 38 points of interest. my first inclination was to think in terms of the sun reflecting off of aircraft coming in and out of lambert international, 12 miles due north of the tower. however, i couldn't account for the now-you-see-it and now-you-don't aspect of the pics; these two disappear and two seconds later two appear somewhere else. also, on very deep zooms it seems there may be a distant light or a light that is coming into focus.
content.summary: Taking pics of a com tower, i observed star-like points of light when editing.

content.detailedDescription: I was in my backyard in monrovia , california monday may 22 at 5:30 pm. i noticed a very bright light very high in the atmosphere that was not moving. it went dull then bright. i got my binoculars and couldn't believe what i saw. it was a triangle shaped "craft". it was too high in the atmosphere to be a plane. i was visible shaken from the sighting.
content.summary: Bright light high in atmosphere- lasted 6 min then disappeared. it was triangle in shape from my binoculars

content.detailedDescription:
15123501788
i was in our backyard playing with our dogs and waterering the yard. i kept feeling like i was being watched from a higher elevation. i assumed one of the neighbors was working on their roof. i turned to look right over our roof and noticed a cloaked shape, sitting in the top of the cloud, immediately. i took several pictures and even my 2 yr old lab/put-mix (dog) was looking up in the exact direction  of the ufo. after about 5 minutes, i went inside to grab my 17 yr old daughter (i figured no one would believe me). we went to the front yard and she immediately saw the same shape trying to cloak itself in the clouds. we watched as two large birds flew toward the ufo and changed direction to avoid the shape. it seemed as if they had not been aware of the ufo until they were approximately 30 ft-40 ft away. after around 20 minutes total it sank down into the puffy cloud and dissipated. we took a few more pictures from the front yard before it disappeared. i felt really sleepy immediately after going inside, but after a 30 minute nap i was really energized the rest of the evening. my daughter felt more energetic following the siting as well. fyi...We live across the highway from dyess afb, and have witnessed several unusual things over the past year.
content.summary: Ufo was cloaked in the top of the only cloud present on a very blue and sunny day. i initially looked up because i felt like i was being watched. several people in town saw it.

content.detailedDescription: I was camping at racliff lake  in campsite 12 and it was about 8 or 9 at night. i was observing the stars when a light blue strobing light appeared behind the trees. it appeared east and my body, laying down with my head looking north, the object moved left made a loop and then disappeared up. in complete awe and with my mouth open i tugged on my girlfriend to look up but it was too late. at first i thought it was a beam of light from a flashlight on the trees but the light shined down not from under or from another side of the lake.
content.summary: Dull yet obvious light hovered and then moved with a loop and disapeared up.

content.detailedDescription: Been witnessing this object for some time. have witnesses that have seen it. watched the object through binocs twice. the lights seem to circle the object changing from red and green and add white after a while. one night while observing through binocs it emitted a white beam. we think it may be a govt. drone but not sure. several of us witnessed a bright white light fly just above our house at an inedible speed one night that was also reported in other towns the same night hundreds of miles from us. the next day the local reporters and papers said it was a meteorite. not so! i have no idea what this object is i've been watching, but it seems to be 'hovering' over formosa plastics alot and south east of our home. are we crazy?? i know what a satellite, plane, and helo looks like at night...And this is not one of those. like i said, i'm not the only one to see it. and it's way too low to be a star. i wouldn't think a drone would have lights? not looking for fame, just want an explanation.
content.summary: Noticed lights in sky that didn't make sense. definitely not a plane or helo.

My mother in law was visiting toronto downtown with my wife. she took some pictures of the buildings on her way home. next day she was showing pictures of downtown buildings to her friends at the esl program where she is studying english, and they noticed that there is was an strange object flying on the sky.

picture is really clear and you can see something flying that looks like an space ship.

content.detailedDescription: I had been staying a couple months at my buddies house in spruce laurel, which i did a lot during hunting season. thanksgiving was coming up soon so my mom came and picked me up. to go back home in quinland. we were driving down the road at jeffrey right before the old sanders grocery store. i looked to my right above the trees and said look mom some ufos.She say the also. there were around 6 to 8 egg shaped glowing orb like spheres. changing from orange,yellow,and red. but staying all the same colors at once in which i described. traveling the same direction and speed that we were going so it seemed.They followed us for around 30 seconds till we got out of long straight strecth .Then lost sight of them over the mountains and tree line. here's where it gets weird or odd me and my mother did not talk about them till 5 years later or more. which is odd that i didn't have here stop the car or anything cause i've always been into ufos an such since i was like 10 or something.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path then hovering
content.summary: Riding with my mom she saw them also

content.detailedDescription:
On vacation in costa rica on pacific side watching a lightning storm at night well offshore, storm was so far away out to sea could not hear the thunder.  snapped about 20 photos of the lightning and this photo immediately caught my attention.  never seen lightning in the shape of round balls, and it also has a strange v shape.  none of the other lightning photos looked anything like this, took the photos over about a 20 minute period.  you can see the palm tree and waves in foreground.

never actually saw the round lights until reviewing photos some minutes later and noticed it looked strange.  please explain how lightning can look like this.  please feel free to examine photo though i would like to remain anonymous.  thanks.
content.summary: Avid lifelong outdoorsman never seen lightning look like this, ever.

content.detailedDescription: When i fist saw the object i was struck by its size and relative brilliance.  my initial thought was that it was the space station but the times i have seen that it was smaller and had a more yellowish/white cast and moved faster.  i pulled out my phone to video but only captured one blurred still.  it moved across the sky, slowed and imploded. there were no sounds.  there was no smoke, no trail and no sign of the object afterwards.  i am an ardent sky watcher and rank this as one of the top four most interesting sightings in my lifetime.  the incident occurred within 1-2 minutes.
content.summary: Orb was moving slowly and steadily from south to north.  looked like an ember/ orangish with aura.  slowed and imploded.

content.detailedDescription: I saw a triangle with orange circle lights on the corners. i was working outside and doing squats looking at the sky. i saw it but got lost in some trees. i am blessed that some one saw it with me (my dad) other wise i would  go mad. i told my family about it. it glided smoothly. the second i saw it i thought it was none other than a ufo it was so distinct how it glided and the lights on it.
content.summary: triangle with light in the corner

content.detailedDescription: I was working in my backyard and looked up above my house at the sky. i noticed a silver very highly reflective object hovering there and watched it stay in the exact same place for about 5 minutes. i thought it may be a balloon until i noticed that it just wasn't moving at all with the wind or anything. it was extremely small because it was quite high so i ran into the house to grab the binoculars. even with those it was still quite difficult to see. i could see however that it had a strange shape, not anything like a balloon would be shaped. the center of it was a flat gray color and the outside had a brilliant shine to it all away around the outline of it. you can see that from the pictures that i took through the binoculars with my cell phone. it was literally not moving long enough in the sky that i could sit there and try and fanangle pictures through my binocular lens! i could also see at times it looked like it was spinning because there was some weird thing at the bottom of it that was sticking out a bit from the rest of it and it looked like above that little thing was movement. it hang there hovering in the same place in the sky for probably 30 minutes or so. then i noticed that it started to move east some slowly. as it was moving east, it must have also been moving further south too because it was getting smaller. then before my eyes the thing just disappeared. i felt very strange watching something like that because it lasted about 45 minutes or so, i couldn't take my eyes off of it. i couldn't figure out how something with no wings could stay in the air like that for so long and so still.
content.summary: Highly reflective hovering object high in the sky

content.detailedDescription:
I had just flown into denver, picked up my car and headed west on i-70.  at about 2:50 pm on a clear day with not much or any wind, i noticed a small object over i-70 from a distance that initially looked like a plastic grocery bag that had been kicked up above i-70 by the wind.  as i move closer, i realize that the bag is floating and not loosing or changing altitude.  i also realize that it is much larger than a small plastic bag and it appears to be a large 15 to 30' oval or rounded rectangular shaped (but not perfectly shaped almost shaped like a smooth irregularly shaped oval floating brown rock) object floating at a consistent altitude and rotating slowly clockwise with a slight wobble. the object looked to be dark brown rather than black, with no markings, windows or lights.  the motion was very consistent with rotation and motion slightly faster than the traffic (15 to 20 mph).   the traffic slowed down as i got closer to the object.  when i got closest to the object, it was on the south side of i-70 moving westerly, slightly faster than the traffic was moving.  five to six lanes of traffic on i-70 bumper to bumper and other people must have seen it and must have reported something to someone.

at 2:58 pm i took my samsung s7 active and turned on the video.  probably the worst video you have seen.  i was driving in the far left lane with cell phone held out of the window. i did capture the object briefly a couple of times during the 32 second video which you will see as a small spec on the screen.  it looks like a small spec on my cell phone and i was just today able to get the video off of my phone and will attach to this report.  i assume with this accurate a location, time, date and the amount of people on i-70 west bound and east bound, there must have been other reports or photos.  was not a plane, bird, drone or insect.  may have been some kind of large balloon filled with helium except for the fact that the rotation and movement west was so smooth and even.  i finally lost sight of the object as it moved west out of my sight.

i was a little bit amazed that i was seeing what really looked like a ufo or some kind of controlled craft (not being blown by the wind).  i tried to use the video on my phone but had a difficult time while driving in stop and go traffic.  i wish that i had fought to get off of the interstate and used a nicer camera that i had in the car but it seemed to difficult to get over from left lane through 6 lanes of traffic to the exit and it may have been gone by the time i made it.  the traffic lightened up or speeded up and i just lost sight of the object in the distance to the west of me and on south side of i-70.
content.summary: West on i-70 in denver west of purina factory.  traffic moving 10 to 20 mph and i-70 packed.  must have been multiple witnesses.  saw floating object over i-70.  round to oval looked like a brown smoothe rock/large balloon rotating slow clockwise.

content.detailedDescription: One night, in about 1992, i was sitting inside watching tv when my father came in from taking the trash down to the curb. he was very excited, saying i had to come out side and see something, but when i asked him what it was, he just said "i don't know". so, i went outside, and found several of our neighbors standing in the street, pointing to the sky. i looked up and saw 4 or 5 huge,oval/disc shaped objects silently hovering in the sky, above the power lines, behind the houses. you could see the object's outline, it's coloring (dark grey) and rectangular shaped lights spaced equally around the perimeter of all of the objects, blink sequentially. one of our neighbors called the police, who came out. they called local airports who said nothing was flying over our area at that time. they said they would file a police report, and they called more police officers out to see the objects. several people stood there watching these objects, staying totally still and silently hovering. then, after 30 to 40 minutes, they all just disappeared. they didn't take off, or fly away, they just disappeared. we all stood there for a while after they left, to see if they returned, and several people said that even though we could no longer see the object, they "felt" like they were still there, maybe just hidden somehow. during all of this, my neighbor was recording with an old vhs camera. the next day she played the tape, only to find the screen was snow, but you could still hear what was going on. this was an incredible, close encounter sighting witnessed by multiple people, including police officers, and i've never understood how it didn't make the news.
content.summary: 4 or 5 huge,disc shaped objects hovering low over power lines for approx 30 minutes, witnessed by several people, including police

content.detailedDescription: This cylinder type craft was flying in a straight line but it was preforming a circular motion i was standing in a friends back garden when we first noticed the cylinder we realised that' it was not a common plane or any other aircraft. the cylinder object was also very high like a plane would be only it was very visible to see as it was very long in ft i estimate this object would have been up to 20 feet long . wee watched the cylinder object as it flew buy it then gained alltatude and desaperd that was the last time we saw the object.
content.summary: It was a cylinder type craft the was flying in a straight line as it was flying it was turning in a circular way
